(secondQuint)A Study Comparing Continuous Sciatic Nerve Block to Single Shot Sciatic Nerve Block.

 There are a limited number of prospective studies in the literature examining the risk of neurologic injury and symptoms after sciatic nerve blocks.

 The incidence of transient neurological symptoms after a continuous catheter is not well reported.

